|   \_____/_/    \_\_|                          |
|                                               |
|  This spell gives you the power to read the   |
|  contents of files                            |
|                                               |
|  Examples                                     |
|                                               |
|  cat wardrobe/cap                             |
|  This will print out the contents of cap if   |
|  you are in ~/my-house/my-room                |
|                                               |
|  cat ~/my-house/my-room/wardrobe/cap          |
|  This will print out the contents of cap      |
|  regardless of where you are                  |
\                                              /
